Write a SQL query that orders items by price. 
SELECT item_name, price
FROM superstore
ORDER BY price desc;

Write a SQL query that will show a stattstc about the item price. 
SELECT AVG (price)
FROM superstore;

Write a SQL query that will show a statistc about the price for items in the category of 'Kitchen Supplies'.
SELECT AVG (price), 'Kitchen Supplies'
FROM superstore;

Write a SQL query that will show the 'Furnishings' products that has a stock quantity less than 40 in ascending order.
SELECT stock_quantity, item_name, 'Furnshngs'
FROM superstore
WHERE stock_quantity < 50
ORDER BY stock_quantity asc;
